A demo project for TDD course using Java

== Development setup ==
1. download Play 1.2.4 http://www.playframework.org/download 
2. add Play to your PATH
3. at project folder in command line, run $> play deps
4. at project folder in command line, run $> play eclipsify 
5. open the project with Eclipse

== Run test ==
1. at project folder in command line, run $> play test
2. visit http://localhost:9000/@tests and Start all tests

== Run server ==
1. at project folder in command line, run $> play run
2. visit http://localhost:9000
